Enum PropertiesTransportOptions.ProjectPropertyType

    Serializable, Comparable<PropertiesTransportOptions.ProjectPropertyType>
    Enclosing interface:
    PropertiesTransportOptions
    public static enum PropertiesTransportOptions.ProjectPropertyType
extends Enum<PropertiesTransportOptions.ProjectPropertyType>
    Enum describing types available for properties transport. Pass these types to PropertiesTransportOptions.setProjectPropertiesTransport(EnumSet) to activate specific properties transport
    Since:
    5.2.21
    See Also:
    PropertiesTransportOptions.setProjectPropertiesTransport(EnumSet)

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant Description
      COMMON
      Type for all common project properties which aren't explicitly specified by an additional enum value of PropertiesTransportOptions.ProjectPropertyType.
      CUSTOM_PROPERTIES
      Use this type to export all custom properties of a project except for this properties .
      FONTS
      Use this type to activate transport of fonts used in belonging project.
      GROUPS
      Use this type to activate transport of user groups used in belonging project.
      LANGUAGES

      MODULE_CONFIGURATIONS

      RESOLUTIONS
      Use this type to activate transport of resolutions used in belonging project.
      SCHEDULE_ENTRIES
      Use this type to activate transport of schedule tasks and templates used in belonging project.
      TEMPLATE_SETS
      Use this type to activate transport of templatesets and presentation channels used in belonging project.
      USERS
      Use this type to activate transport of users used in belonging project.

        public static final PropertiesTransportOptions.ProjectPropertyType COMMON
        Type for all common project properties which aren't explicitly specified by an additional enum value of PropertiesTransportOptions.ProjectPropertyType. Examples for common properties:
        • Project Metadata Template
        • Project release flag
        • Project permission flag
        • Project remote configurations
        Use this type to activate transport of common project properties.

        5.2.21
